m]].\n*[[Women in Islam]].\n*[[Divorce in Islam]].\n*[[Ketubah]], the Jewish marriage contract.\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n*[http://www.muslimwedding.org/yartix.html Articles / Knowledge on Marriage within Islam] at muslimwedding.org\n\n\n[[Category:Islamic jurisprudence]]\n[[Category:Prenuptial agreements]]\n", "name_user": "Rodw", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toBukhari(link changed toSahih al-Bukhari) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Islamic_marriage_contract"}
